data.description: Fantastic Full brick 3 bedroom Harvest home! This home has original hardwood floors and crown molding throughout the entire house!! Eat in kitchen is charming and perfectly updated!  Dining and Living room are open & flooded with natural light. This home has been well cared for and it's completely move-in ready! 1 car garage with w/d hookups. NEW ROOF 12-23! dishwasher is only 1yr old and HVAC system only 2 yrs old. 2012 Vinyl windows, plumbing & electric greatly improves energy efficiency Home sits on 5/8 acre includes a tornado shelter! It is a great place to call home!
